    <!-- Strings für SettingsActivity -->
    <string name="about_this_App">About this App</string>

    <string name="about_this_app_what">What it is about.</string>
    <string name="about_this_app_what_text">This app is called EVENTASTIC. It helps you finding
        upcoming events in your city. Also you can add an event to the list, so that other users of this app can
        participate in it. Once used EVENTASTIC, you will never want to explore the nightlife without it again.</string>

    <string name="about_this_app_how">How to use it.</string>
    <string name="about_this_app_how_text">EVENTASTIC is for free very easy to use. You don´t have to create
        an account and sign in. First, you simply select a CITY or let the app find your position. Then have a look on
        different types of events and click on I WANT TO PARTICIPATE. Your upcoming events will be listed on
        PARTICIPATING EVENTS. That´s it.</string>

    <string name="about_this_app_help">What you can do.</string>
    <string name="about_this_app_help_text">To improve the use of this application, tell your friends and
        family about EVENTASTIC. The more people using this app, the more
        events will be shared and the better for all of us.</string>


